    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 47px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Нотариал идорадан ташқарида жисмоний нуқсони, касаллиги ёки саводсизлиги туфайли ўз қўли билан имзолай олмайдиган шахс номидан бошқа шахс томонидан имзоланган васиятноманинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Васиятнома тасдиқланган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни ушбу васиятномани мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Нотариус Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">.да </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">(</span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#9}Нотариус идорасининг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">-сонли)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> васият қилувчининг хоҳиш-иродасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси қонун ҳужжатларига асосан тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Васиятномани маълум сабабга кўра имзоламаган фуқаронинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Васиятномани имзолай олмаган шахснинг имзолай олмаслик сабаби</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">туфайли унинг шахсий илтимосига кўра васиятномани унинг ўрнига фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Васиятномани имзолаган шахс Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> менинг ҳузуримда ўқиб, имзолади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васият қилувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Васиятномани маълум сабабга кўра имзоламаган фуқаронинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва унинг ўрнига имзо қўйган </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Васиятномани имзолаган шахс Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг шахси аниқланди ва уларнинг муомалага лаёқатлиликлари текширилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Шахсий мулоқот давомида васият қилувчининг ва унинг ўрнига имзо қўйган шахснинг муомалага лаёқатсизлигига шубҳа туғилмади ва ушбу нотариал ҳаракатни амалга ошириш даврида нотариал идорада уларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизликлари ҳақида ҳеч қандай маълумотлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Фуқаролик кодексининг 1128-моддасига асосан васият қилувчининг ўрнига васиятномани имзолаган фуқарога мерос очилгунга қадар васиятноманинг мазмуни, унинг тузилишини ошкор қилишга ҳақли эмаслиги тушунтирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ушбу васиятнома васият қилувчининг касаллиги сабабли унинг таклифига кўра, </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да соат </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Васиятнома тасдиқланган соат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да тасдиқланди</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Реестрга киритилган тартиб рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Давлат божи:</span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Нотариус Ф.И.О</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n</div></div>",
